column2: SELECT  class, survey, instrument, programname,highz_N, dbo.fEBOSSTARGET0N(EBOSS_TARGET0) as EBOSS_TARGET0N FROM ( SELECT  class, survey, instrument, programname, EBOSS_TARGET0, count(z) as highz_N FROM SpecObj WHERE class=&&& AND zWarning = # AND z># AND (survey = &&& OR survey = &&&) AND (programname = &&& OR programname = &&& OR programname = &&&) GROUP BY class,survey,instrument,programname,EBOSS_TARGET0 ) AS inner_list WHERE EBOSS_TARGET0 & (dbo.fEBOSSTARGET0(&&&) | dbo.fEBOSSTARGET0(&&&)) = # ORDER BY programname,highz_N DESC, EBOSS_TARGET0N
